Evolutionary stabilization of the gene-3-protein of phage fd reveals the 
principles that govern the thermodynamic stability of two-domain proteins.

Martin A(1), Schmid FX.

Author information:
(1)Laboratorium für Biochemie und Bayreuther Zentrum für Molekulare 
