Sensor-response regulator interactions in a cross-regulated signal transduction 
network.

Huynh TN(1), Chen LL(2), Stewart V(3).

Author information:
(1)1​ Food Science Graduate Group, University of California, Davis, CA, 
95616-8665, USA.
(2)2​ Department of Microbiology & Molecular Genetics, University of California, 
