divided into groups A (without addition), B, C, D, and E according to the random 
number table, and then the latter 4 groups were respectively cultured with 1.2 
mmol/L CORM-2, 1.6 mmol/L CORM-2, 1.2 mmol/L inactive CORM-2 (iCORM-2), 1.6 
mmol/L iCORM-2, with six samples in each group. After being cultured for 0, 3, 
