A reducing system of the superoxide sensor SoxR in Escherichia coli.

Koo MS(1), Lee JH, Rah SY, Yeo WS, Lee JW, Lee KL, Koh YS, Kang SO, Roe JH.

Author information:
(1)Laboratory of Molecular Microbiology and Laboratory of Biophysics, School of 
Biological Sciences, and Institute of Microbiology, Seoul National University, 
