QseB/QseC regulation in different pathogens and environmental bacteria, the 
functional difference of QseB/QseC among species, and the possibility of 
analyzing QseB/QseC evolution. Here, we discuss the progression of QseB/QseC 
studies and describe several unresolved issues and future directions. Resolving 
these issues is among the challenges of future QseB/QseC studies.

