Epidemiological relationship was analyzed by pulsed-field gel electrophoresis 
(PFGE) and multilocus sequence typing (MLST). Conjugation experiments were 
performed to determine the transferability of plasmids. Whole-genome sequencing 
(WGS) of strains was implemented, and the genetic environment of the bla NDM-1- 
and mcr-9-carrying plasmids was analyzed.
