isolates harbored multiple resistance genes. ECL68 and ECL78 co-produce bla 
NDM-1 and mcr-9. Among the four different sequence types (STs) detected, ST1466 
was assigned as a novel ST. Six isolates exhibited highly similar PFGE patterns. 
