the two isolates, ECL68 and ECL78. In ECL68, bla NDM-1 and mcr-9 were present on 
the same plasmid while located in two separate plasmids in ECL78. The genetic 
environment of mcr-9 was organized as IS26-wbuC-mcr-9-IS903-pcoS-pcoE-rcnA-rcnR, 
