The Xanthomonas campestris rpsM (S13)-rpsK (S11)-rpsD (S4)-rpoA (alpha)-rplQ 
(L17) cluster, encoding RNA polymerase alpha-subunit and four ribosomal 
proteins, reside in a 3164-bp DNA region. The N-terminal sequence of the 
