mutants, which include all two-component regulatory systems of Escherichia coli, 
under a single growth condition. DNA microarray results revealed that the 
mutants belong to one of three groups based on their gene expression profiles in 
Luria-Bertani broth under aerobic conditions: (i) those with no or little 
