interaction between YccT and CsgA was detected. Thus, YccT-renamed CsgI (curli 
synthesis inhibitor)-is a novel inhibitor of curli fimbriae formation and has a 
dual role as an OmpR phosphorylation modulator and CsgA polymerization 
inhibitor.

