adaptation of this bacterium to high osmotic stress. The overall impact of OmpR 
on the various metabolic and regulatory systems of A. caldus was revealed by 
transcriptome analysis. The OmpR binding sequences of differentially expressed 
genes (DEGs) were predicted, and the OmpR box motif in A. caldus was analysed. 
