cellular ribosomal protein levels, thereby suggesting that mRNA processing is 
involved in tuning growth-dependent ribosome synthesis. In conclusion, our 
findings suggest that mRNA processing-mediated post-transcriptional regulation 
is a potential mechanism of ribosomal protein synthesis and stoichiometry.

