The ruvC gene of Escherichia coli specifies a nuclease that resolves Holliday 
junction intermediates in genetic recombination (B. Connolly, C.A. Parsons, F.E. 
Benson, H.J. Dunderdale, G.J. Sharples, R.G. Lloyd, and S.C. West, Proc. Natl. 
