genes probably form an operon. However, expression of ruvC was found to be very 
poor relative to that of orf-33. A double ribosomal frameshift between these 
genes is proposed as a possible reason for the low level of RuvC. Two further 
open reading frames of unknown function were identified, one on either side of 
the orf-33-ruvC operon.

